XX/XX/2016 - libbitcoin-server version 3 release.

  * ZMQ Tor support.
  * Integrated tx radar (send notifications) and improved broadcasting
    capability.
  * Dynamically configurable blockchain parameters. Through config files run
    mainnet, testnet or alternative blockchains.
  * Highly efficient implementation (TODO: post numbers).
    Uses asynchronous callback based code for highly scalable parallelization.

